{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856777978,"sessionID":"ses_286b066a1ffeuIkVCINkfD0aS1","part":{"id":"prt_d794ff550001TiLrL4iIVXI4S3","messageID":"msg_d794fed6b001tkHHE3hJy8ENwK","sessionID":"ses_286b066a1ffeuIkVCINkfD0aS1","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-92651ac082284957b98543e2d3fc56a0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/CHANGE.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/CHANGE.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-013 — Redis 存储实现\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: - **AR**: AR-013\n5: - **Title**: Redis 存储实现\n6: - **Module**: pkg/store\n7: - **Language**: Go\n8: - **Size**: M\n9: - **Status**: Pending\n10: \n11: ## Description\n12: Implement the Redis storage provider for the AgentCube session store interface.\n13: \n14: ## Dependencies\n15: - AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n16: \n17: ## Related Changes\n18: None\n\n(End of file - total 18 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-013 — Redis 存储实现\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-013\n- **Title**: Redis 存储实现\n- **Module**: pkg/store\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\nImplement the Redis storage provider for the AgentCube session store interface.\n\n## Dependencies\n- AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n\n## Related Changes\nNone","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775856777950,"end":1775856777976}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775856777981,"sessionID":"ses_286b066a1ffeuIkVCINkfD0aS1","part":{"id":"prt_d794ff825001SmADeI5iu2aQQk","messageID":"msg_d794fed6b001tkHHE3hJy8ENwK","sessionID":"ses_286b066a1ffeuIkVCINkfD0aS1","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-7c92a2437e9f4454b334fb99b43e7fcf","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-013 Delta-Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: Implement the Redis storage provider for the AgentCube session store interface, providing a concrete implementation of the Store interface defined in AR-012.\n5: \n6: ## Base Specs\n7: - AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n8: - deployment/client-go.md: Kubernetes client library for runtime API types\n9: - session-store/design.md: Session store design including Store interface and Redis implementation\n10: - session-store/spec.md: Session store specification with detailed requirements\n11: \n12: ## Requirements\n13: \n14: ### Requirement: Redis client initialization\n15: The system SHALL initialize a Redis client using `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` with configuration from environment variables.\n16: \n17: #### Scenario: Basic Redis client setup\n18: - **GIVEN** valid `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` environment variables\n19: - **WHEN** the Redis store is initialized\n20: - **THEN** a Redis client is created with the configured address and password\n21: \n22: ### Requirement: Store interface implementation\n23: The system SHALL implement the Store interface using Redis client for all required methods.\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: Ping method implementation\n26: - **GIVEN** a healthy Redis connection\n27: - **WHEN** `Ping(ctx)` is called\n28: - **THEN** it returns nil after successful PING command\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: GetSandboxBySessionID implementation\n31: - **GIVEN** a session key exists in Redis\n32: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, id)` is called\n33: - **THEN** it retrieves and unmarshals the SandboxInfo JSON\n34: \n35: #### Scenario: StoreSandbox implementation\n36: - **GIVEN** a valid SandboxInfo\n37: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)` is called\n38: - **THEN** it stores the JSON and updates indices atomically\n39: \n40: ### Requirement: Environment variable configuration\n41: The system SHALL read and validate Redis connection parameters from environment variables.\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: Missing required environment variables\n44: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` is not set\n45: - **WHEN** Redis store initialization is attempted\n46: - **THEN** it returns an error indicating the missing required variable\n47: \n48: ### Requirement: Error handling\n49: The system SHALL properly handle Redis errors and convert them to appropriate package-level errors.\n50: \n51: #### Scenario: Redis connection error\n52: - **GIVEN** Redis server is unreachable\n53: - **WHEN** any store operation is called\n54: - **THEN** it returns a connection error\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: Key not found\n57: - **GIVEN** a session key does not exist in Redis\n58: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID` is called\n59: - **THEN** it returns `ErrNotFound`\n60: \n61: ### Requirement: Atomic operations\n62: The system SHALL use Redis pipelines for multi-command operations to ensure atomicity.\n63: \n64: #### Scenario: StoreSandbox atomicity\n65: - **GIVEN** a valid SandboxInfo\n66: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` executes\n67: - **THEN** all Redis commands execute in a single pipeline\n68: \n69: ### Requirement: Connection lifecycle\n70: The system SHALL properly manage Redis connection lifecycle including initialization and cleanup.\n71: \n72: #### Scenario: Close method\n73: - **GIVEN** an active Redis connection\n74: - **WHEN** `Close()` is called\n75: - **THEN** the Redis client connection is closed\n\n(End of file - total 75 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-013 Delta-Spec\n\n## Purpose\nImplement the Redis storage provider for the AgentCube session store interface, providing a concrete implementation of the Store interface defined in AR-012.\n\n## Base Specs\n- AR-012: 会话存储接口定义\n- deployment/client-go.md: Kubernetes client library for runtime API types\n- session-store/design.md: Session store design including Store interface and Redis implementation\n- session-store/spec.md: Session store specification with detailed requirements\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Redis client initialization\nThe system SHALL initialize a Redis client using `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` with configuration from environment variables.\n\n#### Scenario: Basic Redis client setup\n- **GIVEN** valid `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` environment variables\n- **WHEN** the Redis store is initialized\n- **THEN** a Redis client is created with the configured address and password","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775856777953,"end":1775856777979}}}}
